LOCUS       SpyTag003                 16 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  SpyTag003 - 16-aa peptide (RGVPHIVMVDAYKRYK), third-generation
            reactive Spy peptide that forms a spontaneous, irreversible
            isopeptide bond to SpyCatcher003 at near-diffusion-limited speed
            (~5.5e5 M-1 s-1)..
